    <div id="main-hed"> 
     <h1>Life's Decisions Made Here</h1> 
     <h2>When faced with life's most important choices, people look for guidance from the trusted advice and rankings of U.S. News &amp; World Report.</h2> 
    </div> 
    <!-- main-hed --> 
    <div id="index-about" class="clear"> 
     <h3>About U.S. News &amp; World Report</h3> 
     <p>For over 80 years, U.S. News &amp; World Report has been a publisher of news and information that empowers people to make better, more informed decisions about important issues affecting their lives. By delivering credible analysis and guidance, U.S. News has become one of the fastest growing news and information brands.</p> 
    </div> 
    <div class="rule-above clear"> 
     <h3>Rankings &amp; Consumer Advice</h3> 
