    </div> 
    <div class="rule-above clear"> 
     <img src="images/HP_news.png" class="right"> 
     <div id="index-left"> 
      <h3>News Authority Since 1933</h3> 
      <p>U.S. News brings an objective, informative and 360-degree perspective to today’s complex stories. From historical milestones to current events, the news team takes an in-depth approach to covering the top national agenda issues through analysis, opinion, data, photography, video, special reports and more.</p> 
     </div> 
    </div> 
    <div class="rule-above clear"> 
     <img src="images/HP_Guidebooks.png" class="left"> 
     <div id="index-right"> 
      <h3>A Research-Minded Audience</h3> 
      <p>U.S. News is an information destination for educated professionals, business leaders and policy makers. With 149 million page views per month, these engaged visitors rely on U.S. News for help and advice while facing important decisions such as applying to college or buying a car.</p> 
      <p class="link"><a href="audience">Learn more about our audience&nbsp;»</a></p> 
     </div> 
    </div> 
    <div id="index-adops" class="rule-above clear"> 
     <h3>Unique Ad Opportunities</h3> 
     <p>U.S. News offers a variety of custom ad placements that provide premium brands the opportunity to showcase their message in an engaging and meaningful way. From native advertising to unique sponsorships, U.S. News helps brands achieve their goals by reaching an on-task, research-minded audience.</p> 
     <p class="link"><a href="ad-specs">Learn more about our custom ad opportunities&nbsp;»</a></p> 
